        KEYWORDS="xfce"
           SHORT="XFce4 XKB Layout Switch panel plugin"
cat << EOF
This plugin displays the current keyboard layout, and refreshes when layout
changes. Also the layout can be switched by simply clicking on the plugin. The
new version can display the layout as text label and also as an image of the
corresponding country's flag. If the flag image is unavailable then the plugin
falls back to displaying text label for that layout.
EOF
